<a href='http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/1908/universe_sandbox11'><img width="150" height="150" src="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/universe_sandbox11-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="universe_sandbox11" /></a>
